%20the%20monthly%20job%20reports%20but%20keep%20publishing%20the%20more%20accurate%2C%20though%20less%20timely%2C%20quarterly%20data.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEconomists%20and%20market%20strategists%20told%20Business%20Insider%20on%20Tuesday%20that%20such%20a%20move%20would%20be%20damaging%20for%20investors%20and%20economic%20planners.%20It%20could%20lower%20trust%20in%20the%20timeliest%20data%20on%20unemployment%20and%20job%20growth%2C%20which%20gives%20insight%20into%20how%20corporate%20earnings%20will%20perform%20and%20the%20broader%20state%20of%20the%20US%20economy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20markets%20depend%20on%20employment%20reports%20and%20the%20inflation%20reports%20and%20those%20types%20of%20things%20for%20direction%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Lance%20Roberts%2C%20the%20chief%20strategist%20at%20RIA%20Advisors%2C%20which%20manages%20%242%20billion.%20%26quot%3BYou%20try%20to%20suspend%20that%20data%2C%20without%20really%20good%20reason%2C%20that's%20going%20to%20cause%20problems%20for%20markets.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERoberts%20said%20that%20it's%20important%20to%20keep%20the%20monthly%20pace%20for%20the%20non-farm%20payrolls%20report%2C%20and%20that%20revisions%20are%20part%20of%20the%20data-collection%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20revise%20GDP%20data%20every%20year%2C%20and%20then%20we%20revise%20it%20every%20three%20years%2C%20and%20the%20markets%20never%20freak%20out%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20adding%3A%20%26quot%3BMarkets%20run%20real-time%2C%20they%20need%20real-time%20data.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMax%20Stier%2C%20the%20president%20and%20CEO%20of%20Partnership%20for%20Public%20Service%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20BLS%20data%20plays%20a%20key%20role%20in%20both%20the%20overall%20economy%20and%20people's%20financial%20decisions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20imperative%20that%20the%20bureau%20continues%20to%20report%20this%20information%20in%20a%20timely%2C%20unbiased%20way%20to%20preserve%20its%20trustworthiness%20as%20an%20institution%2C%26quot%3B%20Stier%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStier%20added%20that%20if%20Antoni%20is%20confirmed%20by%20the%20Senate%20to%20take%20on%20the%20commissioner%20role%2C%20he%20urges%20%26quot%3BAntoni%20to%20partner%20with%20the%20bureau's%20expert%20civil%20service%20to%20maintain%20the%20nonpartisan%20collection%20and%20presentation%20of%20their%20economic%20data.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EElizabeth%20Renter%2C%20senior%20economist%20at%20NerdWallet%2C%20said%20the%20monthly%20jobs%20data%20shouldn't%20be%20suspended%20or%20delayed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20biggest%20revisions%20to%20jobs%20data%20often%20happen%20when%20the%20economy%20hits%20a%20turning%20point%20%E2%80%94%20economists%20and%20economic%20policymakers%20largely%20understand%20this%2C%26quot%3B%20Renter%20said.%20%26quot%3BTo%20slow%20the%20availability%20of%20the%20data%20at%20such%20a%20juncture%20could%20severely%20hamper%20the%20ability%20of%20the%20Fed%20to%20conduct%20effective%20monetary%20policy%2C%20among%20other%20things.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENot%20everyone%20agrees%2C%20however.%20Irene%20Tunkel%2C%20the%20chief%20strategist%20of%20US%20equity%20strategy%20at%20BCA%20Research%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20on%20Tuesday%20that%20moving%20to%20a%20quarterly%20pace%20where%20the%20BLS%20has%20more%20time%20to%20survey%20businesses%20would%20be%20a%20better%20approach.%20Theoretically%2C%20a%20quarterly%20cadence%20would%20result%20in%20fewer%20revisions%2C%20Tunkel%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20market%20can%20rely%20on%20private%20data%20from%20sources%20like%20ADP%20for%20more%20real-time%20information.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20private%20data%20sources%20don't%20have%20the%20funding%20that%20the%20BLS%20does%2C%20and%20are%20therefore%20even%20less%20reliable%2C%20said%20Preston%20Caldwell%2C%20a%20US%20economist%20at%20Morningstar.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20markets%20believed%20the%20CES%20conveyed%20no%20useful%20information%2C%20they%20would%20already%20ignore%20it%20%E2%80%94%20no%20damage%20done.%20So%20why%20suspend%20it%3F%20There's%20not%20a%20good%20substitute%20for%20the%20CES%2C%26quot%3B%20Caldwell%20wrote%20in%20an%20email%2C%20referencing%20the%20Current%20Employment%20Statistics%20survey%20that%20produces%20the%20monthly%20job%20creation%20numbers%20from%20the%20BLS.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20there%20was%20a%20cheap%20way%20to%20do%20it%2C%20a%20third-party%20data%20provider%20might%20be%20doing%20it%20already.%20But%20that's%20not%20the%20case.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%221cb19779-affe-4eea-8629-1c07fd33c9cb%5C%22%3EAntoni's%20comments%20follow%20a%20worse-than-expected%20July%20jobs%20report%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAntoni%20was%20nominated%20to%20the%20BLS%20role%20on%20August%2011%20after%20Trump%20fired%20former%20commissioner%20and%20Biden%20appointee%20Dr.%20Erika%20McEntarfer%20on%20August%201.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20Economy%20is%20booming%2C%20and%20E.J.%20will%20ensure%20that%20the%20Numbers%20released%20are%20HONEST%20and%20ACCURATE%2C%26quot%3B%20Trump%20wrote%20in%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftruthsocial.com%2F%40realDonaldTrump%2F115012532470689820%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETruth%20Social%20post%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20disappointing%20jobs%20report%20showed%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-economic-outlook-stagflation-boom-inflation-growth-bank-of-america-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_self%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EUS%20economy%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20added%2073%2C000%20jobs%20in%20July%2C%20missing%20the%20consensus%20106%2C000%2C%20and%20revisions%20to%20the%20previous%20two%20months%20showed%20there%20were%20way%20fewer%20jobs%20added%20than%20earlier%20reported.%20Revisions%20are%20a%20normal%20part%20of%20the%20BLS%20data%20collection%2C%20though%20the%20agency%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Freal-problem-america-jobs-data-bls-funding-trump-fired-commissioner-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ehas%20struggled%20in%20recent%20years%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20limited%20resources%20and%20declining%20survey%20response%20rates.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20president%20claimed%20that%20the%20data%20was%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftruthsocial.com%2F%40realDonaldTrump%2Fposts%2F114955222046259464%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERIGGED%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20order%20to%20make%20the%20Republicans%2C%20and%20ME%2C%20look%20bad.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E'%26quot%3BHow%20on%20earth%20are%20businesses%20supposed%20to%20plan%20%E2%80%94%20or%20how%20is%20the%20Fed%20supposed%20to%20conduct%20monetary%20policy%20%E2%80%94%20when%20they%20don't%20know%20how%20many%20jobs%20are%20being%20added%20or%20lost%20in%20our%20economy%3F%20It's%20a%20serious%20problem%20that%20needs%20to%20be%20fixed%20immediately%2C%26quot%3B%20Antoni%20told%20Fox%20News%20Digital%2C%20adding%2C%20%26quot%3Bmajor%20decision-makers%20from%20Wall%20Street%20to%20D.C.%20rely%20on%20these%20numbers%2C%20and%20a%20lack%20of%20confidence%20in%20the%20data%20has%20far-reaching%20consequences.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAntoni%20has%20not%20yet%20been%20confirmed%20as%20commissioner.%20The%20Heritage%20Foundation%20and%20BLS%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Edid%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20Business%20Insider's%20requests%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHiding%20the%20numbers%20just%20makes%20it%20that%20much%20harder%20to%20use%20the%20tools%20available%20to%20avoid%20further%20economic%20pain%2C%20prepare%20for%20what%20people%20need%2C%20and%20guard%20against%20a%20recession%2C%26quot%3B%20former%20acting%20Secretary%20of%20Labor%20Julie%20Su%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAsked%20whether%20the%20BLS%20would%20continue%20to%20put%20out%20a%20monthly%20payrolls%20report%2C%20White%20House%20press%20secretary%20Karoline%20Leavitt%20said%20in%20a%20press%20conference%20on%20Tuesday%20that%20she%20believes%20that%20will%20be%20the%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20believe%20that%20is%20the%20plan%20and%20that's%20the%20hope%20and%20that%20these%20monthly%20reports%20will%20be%20data%20that%20the%20American%20people%20can%20trust%2C%26quot%3B%20Leavitt%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-bls-nominee-suggests-halting-monthly-jobs-report-2025-8%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1755029745000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F689b67a2194a2d49b8ae6a07%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-bls-nominee-suggests-halting-monthly-jobs-report-2025-8%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22E.J.%20Antoni%2C%20President%20Trump's%20pick%20to%20lead%20the%20Bureau%20of%20Labor%20Statistics%2C%20said%20it%20should%20suspend%20the%20monthly%20jobs%20report%20over%20accuracy%20concerns.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22allisonkelly%40businessinsider.com%20(Allie%20Kelly%2CJuliana%20Kaplan%2CWilliam%20Edwards%2CMadison%20Hoff)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A810%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-bls-nominee-suggests-halting-monthly-jobs-report-2025-8%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Romanian%20Director%20Andrei%20Epure%20Drills%20Down%20on%20%E2%80%98Sabotaging%20Realism%E2%80%99%20in%20His%20Locarno%20Player%20%E2%80%98Don%E2%80%99t%20Let%20Me%20Die%E2%80%99%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1755029704000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FDont-Let-Me-Die-still-1.jpg%3Fw%3D1000%26h%3D563%26crop%3D1%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F%3Fp%3D1236487739%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Expanding%20on%20the%20world%20built%20in%20his%202021%20short%20%E2%80%9CIntercom%2015%2C%E2%80%9D%20Andrei%20Epure%E2%80%99s%20debut%20feature%20%E2%80%9CDon%E2%80%99t%20Let%20Me%20Die%E2%80%9D%20is%20an%2