0competing%20claims%20on%20being%20needed.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20our%20middle-aged%20bodies%20and%20minds%20are%20tug-of-war%20in%20two%20directions.%20My%20husband%20is%20completely%20gray%3B%20he%20ignores%20his%20rising%20blood%20pressure%2C%20and%20I%20ignore%20an%20aching%20hip%2C%20disobedient%20hormones%2C%20and%20brain%20fog.%20We%20can%20never%20truly%20switch%20off%20and%20always%20being%20%26quot%3Bon%20call%26quot%3B%20takes%20its%20toll.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20can't%20throw%20caution%20to%20the%20wind%2C%20turn%20off%20our%20phones%2C%20or%20go%20off-grid%20for%20a%20day%3B%20there%20may%20be%20a%20person%20who%20needs%20us.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22d5cd80b5-77e7-4608-b8d4-3181cd85486f%5C%22%3EI%20carry%20a%20lot%20of%20guilt%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20also%20the%20guilt%20%E2%80%94%20mother's%20guilt%20and%20daughter's%20guilt.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAm%20I%20a%20good%20enough%20mom%3F%20Am%20I%20too%20much%20a%20friend%2C%20not%20enough%20a%20parent%3F%20Should%20I%20have%20cried%20in%20front%20of%20the%20kids%3F%20Should%20their%20dad%20and%20I%20have%20argued%20in%20front%20of%20them%3F%20What%20about%20the%20time%20I%20got%20blackout%20drunk%20at%20a%20party%20and%20they%20saw%20me%20puke%20in%20the%20driveway%3F%20An%20endless%20list%20of%20self-flagellation%20that%20every%20parent%20will%20recognize.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20same%20time%2C%20there's%20the%20daughter's%20guilt.%20Am%20I%20visiting%20my%20parents%20enough%3F%20Am%20I%20calling%20enough%3F%20Should%20I%20be%20running%20daily%20casseroles%20over%20to%20them%3F%20Should%20I%20be%20insisting%20they%20wear%20a%20personal%20alarm%20that%20directly%20alerts%20the%20emergency%20services%3F%20And%20if%20I'm%20honest%2C%20I%20feel%20guilt%20at%20the%20anger%20I%20feel%20when%20I%20see%20them%20getting%20older%20and%20weaker.%20Anger%20at%20them%20for%20allowing%20themselves%20to%20age%2C%20allowing%20themselves%20to%20one%20day%20be%20taken%20from%20us.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn