%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6859750985e81483682c902d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222667%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20Tesla%20Robotaxi%20on%20the%20streets%20in%20Austin.%20The%20service%20launched%20in%20limited%20form%20on%20June%2022%2C%202025.%3Cp%3EJoel%20Angel%20Juarez%2FREUTERS%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ETesla%20is%20offering%20up%20to%20%2433.66%20an%20hour%20base%20pay%20to%20robotaxi%20test%20drivers%20in%20NYC%2C%20job%20listings%20show.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EDrivers%20need%20to%20be%20%26quot%3Btech-savvy%26quot%3B%20and%20familiar%20with%20autonomous%20driving.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20move%20comes%20as%20the%20robotaxi%20competition%20heats%20up%2C%20though%20Tesla%20hasn't%20applied%20for%20permits%20in%20NYC.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ENew%20York%20City%20streets%3A%20honking%20cabs%2C%20zig-zagging%20delivery%20bikes%2C%20pedestrians%20with%20little%20respect%20for%20traffic%20lights%2C%20and%2C%20perhaps%20soon%2C%20Tesla%20robotaxi%20testers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20Tesla%20lays%20the%20groundwork%20to%20expand%20its%20robotaxi%20service%20to%20more%20US%20cities%2C%20recent%20job%20listings%20indicate%20that%20it's%20hiring%20autonomous%20vehicle%20operators%20in%20the%20Big%20Apple%20to%20help%20it%20do%20so.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETesla%20is%20hiring%20prototype%20vehicle%20operators%20in%20Queens%2C%20New%20York%2C%20to%20operate%20engineering%20cars%20with%20%26quot%3Bautonomous%20driving%20systems%26quot%3B%20and%20collect%20driving%20data%2C%20according%20to%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tesla.com%2Fcareers%2Fsearch%2Fjob%2Fvehicle-operator-autopilot-247006%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ejob%20listing%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20the%20company's%20website%20titled%20%26quot%3BVehicle%20Operator%2C%20Autopilot.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20gig%20pays%20up%20to%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2433.66%20an%20hour%2C%20but%20not%20all%20drivers%20will%20be%20paid%20the%20same%20amount%2C%20according%20to%20the%20posting.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20Test%20Operator%20I%20can%20make%20between%20%2425.25%20and%20%2427.60%20an%20hour%20base%20pay%2C%20while%20a%20Test%20Operator%20II%20drivers%20earn%20between%20%2428.75%20and%20%2430.60%20an%20hour%20base%20(minimum%20wage%20for%20large%20employers%20in%20New%20York%20City%20is%20%2416.50).%20Anyone%20working%20an%20afternoon%20or%20night%20shift%20makes%2010%25%20more%20than%20the%20base%20pay%2C%20which%20would%20bring%20the%20hourly%20pay%20up%20to%20%2433.66%20at%20the%20highest%20pay%20range%2C%20and%20all%20are%20eligible%20for%20Tesla%20benefits.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EApplicants%20should%20be%20able%20to%20work%20a%20%26quot%3Bflexible%20schedule%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20posting%20says%2C%20including%20availability%20on%20one%20weekend%20day.%20The%20gig%20is%20either%20Tuesday%20through%20Saturday%20or%20Sunday%20through%20Thursday%2C%20with%20two%20different%20day%2C%20afternoon%2C%20and%20night%20shifts%20available.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20not%20just%20driving%20a%20car%20%E2%80%94%20those%20who%20get%20the%20gig%20will%20need%20to%20operate%20recording%20devices%2C%20debug%20software%20as%20needed%2C%20collect%20and%20analyze%20audio%20and%20camera%20data%2C%20and%20give%20detailed%20feedback.%20The%20ideal%20applicant%20has%20to%20have%20good%20English%20communication%20skills%2C%20be%20%26quot%3Btech-savvy%20with%20experience%20managing%20tools%20for%20data%20collection%20and%20troubleshooting%20with%20advanced%20PC%20skills%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20be%20familiar%20with%20autonomous%20driving%20systems.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETesla%20is%20also%20hiring%20test%20drivers%20in%20other%20cities%2C%20with%20job%20postings%20listed%20in%20Texas%2C%20Florida%2C%20and%20California.%20The%20electric%20vehicles%20news%20outlet%20InsideEVs%20previously%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Finsideevs.com%2Fnews%2F767764%2Ftesla-robotaxi-new-york-hiring%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20Tesla%20was%20also%20hiring%20drivers