%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.amazon.com%252Fdp%252FB0F38G9DLV%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EVivoactive%206%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20going%20to%20be%20a%20better%20pick%20%E2%80%94%20at%20a%20better%20price%20%E2%80%94%20for%20the%20majority%20of%20people%20looking%20for%20a%20smart%20fitness%20watch.%20(Check%20out%20our%20full%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fgarmin-vivoactive-6-review%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EVivoactive%206%20review%3C%2Fa%3E.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20Venu%203%20is%20all-in-all%20a%20solid%20watch%2C%20after%20testing%20it%20for%20the%20last%20few%20months%2C%20I%20don't%20think%20it's%20the%20best%20value%20for%20your%20money.%20Here's%20why.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%221962654f-68da-4314-8c1e-c3abb0f94b6d%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22What%20we%20like%5C%22%3EWhat%20I%20found%20after%203%20months%20of%20testing%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%226ea7e4a8-4bbf-4c0c-9192-2e71f26f094b%5C%22%3EIt's%20built%20on%20Garmin's%20fitness%20tracking%20power.%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EGarmin%20has%20some%20of%20the%20best%20fitness%20tracking%20technology%2C%20based%20on%20a%20long-standing%20foundation%20of%20very%20accurate%20GPS%20and%20heart%20rate%20detection.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20this%20core%2C%20the%20Venu%203%20has%20a%20lot%20of%20the%20same%20features%20and%20abilities%20that%20make%20Garmin's%20other%20lifestyle%20watches%20great%20for%20fitness%20devotees%3A%20it%20tracks%20your%20steps%2C%20sleep%2C%20and%20stress%20automatically%3B%20has%2030%20pre-loaded%20activity%20profiles%20you%20can%20manually%20use%20to%20track%20workouts%20with%20helpful%20in-the-moment%20stats%20like%20heart%20rate%2C%20pace%2C%20and%20distance%3B%20it%20uses%20your%20health%20and%20activity%20data%20to%20determine%20your%20%26quot%3Bbody%20battery%26quot%3B%20energy%20and%20recovery%20levels%20throughout%20the%20day%3B%20and%20it%20has%20a%20digital%20coach%20for%20training%20and%20improving%20your%20sleep.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEvery%20morning%2C%20the%20Venu%203%20delivers%20a%20morning%20report%20with%20sleep%20quality%2C%20body%20battery%2C%20and%20a%20daily%20suggested%20workout.%20And%2C%20like%20most%20every%20Garmin%20watch%2C%20the%20face%20and%20data%20fields%20are%20fully%20customizable%20in%20the%20app%20so%20you%20can%20tweak%20the%20watch%20to%20match%20your%20needs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2215030621-429b-4c44-a597-009f8f4330ef%5C%22%3EIt's%20sleek%2C%20intuitive%2C%20and%20has%20a%20great%20battery%20life.%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Venu%203%2C%20like%20most%20Garmin%20models%2C%20has%20many%20other%20perks%20than%20the%20foundational%20tech%3A%20It%20has%20an%20exceptionally%20long%20battery%20life%20(14%20days%20in%20smartwatch%20mode%2C%20or%2026%20hours%20in%20GPS%20mode)%2C%20which%20means%20you%20can%20more%20continuously%20track%20sleep%20and%20daytime%20stress%2C%20and%20you%20can%20leave%20your%20charger%20behind%20for%20short%20travels.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20side-by-side%20image%20of%20a%20Garmin%20smartwatch%20on%20a%20light%20wooden%20surface.%20The%20left%20side%20shows%20the%20front%20of%20the%20watch%20with%20a%20round%20display%20featuring%20a%20purple-themed%20analog%20watch%20face%20and%20widgets.%20The%20right%20side%20shows%20the%20back%20of%20the%20watch%2C%20revealing%20its%20sensors%20glowing%20green%20and%20contact%20points%20for%20charging.%20The%20watch%20has%20a%20white%20silicone%20strap.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6894d5b3cfc04e97619b050d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Garmin%20Venu%203%20comes%20in%20two%20sizes.%20I%20tried%20the%2041mm%20version%20(called%20the%20Venu%203S)%2C%20shown%20here.%20Both%20sizes%20function%20the%20same.%3Cp%3EShannon%20Ullman%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20AMOLED%20display%20is%20crisp%20and%20vivid%2C%20the%20interface%20intuitive%2C%20and%20the%20case%20design%20more%20refined%20than%20past%20Garmin%20watches%20(though%20it%20looks%20very%20similar%20to%20the%20Vivoactive%206).%20You%20can%20customize%20the%20watch%20face%20so%20it%20looks%20as%20sporty%20or%20as%20sleek%20as%20you%20prefer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20also%20appreciate%20that%20it%20comes%20in%20two%20sizes%2C%20the%20smaller%20Venu%203S%20with%20a%2041mm%20screen%20and%20the%20Venu%203%20with%20a%2045mm%20screen.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%220f69fd9a-f507-44c3-ae3e-6ce14852c418%5C%22%3EIt's%20a%20smarter%20watch%E2%80%A6sort%20of.%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20biggest%20headline%20that%20sets%20the%20Venu%203%20apart%20from%20Garmin's%20other%20watches%20is%20that%20it%20has%20a%20built-in%20microphone%20and%20speaker.%20This%20means%20you%20can%20take%20calls%20and%20use%20your%20phone's%20voice%20assistant%20directly%20from%20your%20wrist%20%E2%80%94%20something%20the%20Vivoactive%206%20and%20Garmin's%20less-smart%20watches%20can't%20do.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20one%20hand%2C%20I%20found%20this%20feature%20genuinely%20convenient%20during%20moments%20like%20taking%20quick%20%26quot%3Bneed%20anything%20on%20my%20way%20home%26quot%3B%20calls%20from%20my%20husband%2C%20or%20replying%20to%20a%20text%20while%20hands-deep%20in%20pie%20crust.%20A%20quick%20voice%20reply%20definitely%20beats%20tracking%20down%20my%20phone%20for%20a%20short%20answer%20or%20trying%20to%20swipe%20with%20messy%20fingers.%20I%20also%20found%20the%20voice-to-text%20feature%20worked%20just%20as%20well%20(if%20not%20better)%20than%20using%20Siri%20to%20dictate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20Garmin%20Venu%203%20smartwatch%20is%20shown%20on%20a%20person's%20wrist%2C%20displaying%20a%20text%20message%20notification%20from%20someone%20named%20Chris%2C%20whose%20name%20is%20followed%20by%20a%20cat%20emoji.%20The%20message%20reads%2C%20%26quot%3BWhat%20time%20do%20you%20want%20to%20get%20dinner%3F%26quot%3B%20The%20watch%20has%20a%20white%20band%20and%20a%20round%20face%20with%20a%20black%20screen%20and%20gold%20bezel%2C%20and%20it%20is%20set%20against%20a%20white%20fabric%20background.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F689b6001a17a8c5b4052b64e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222268%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Venu%203%20lets%20you%20reply%20to%20texts%20as%20they%20come%20in%2C%20but%20you'll%20need%20to%20keep%20your%20phone%20unlocked%20to%20initiate%20new%20texts.%3Cp%3ERachael%20Schultz%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20said%2C%20there's%20a%20big%20catch%3A%20your%20phone%20has%20to%20be%20unlocked%20for%20you%20to%20do%20anything%20beyond%20responding%20to%20an%20incoming%20text%20or%20answering%20a%20call.%20Unlike%20with%2C%20say%2C%20an%20Apple%20Watch%2C%20the%20Venu%203%20can't%20initiate%20a%20text%20to%20someone%2C%20reply%20to%20a%20text%20from%20earlier%20in%20the%20day%2C%20or%20even%20add%20something%20to%20your%20Notes%20app%20without%20your%20phone%20being%20unlocked%20first.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20found%20this%20to%20be%20quite%20frustrating%3B%20this%20limitation%20really%20narrowed%20how%20often%20the%20on-wrist%20reply%20function%20was%20actually%20usable.%20The%20voice%20assistant%20access%20was%20also%20finicky%20%E2%80%94%20sometimes%20I'd%20press%20and%20hold%20the%20middle%20button%20and%20it%20would%20say%20%26quot%3Bconnecting%20to%20voice%20assistant%2C%26quot%3B%20only%20to%20immediately%20go%20back%20to%20the%20home%20screen.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20short%2C%20it's%20not%20quite%20the%20seamless%20smart%20assistant%20experience%20you%20get%20from%20an%20Apple%20Watch%20or%20Galaxy%20Watch.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you're%20an%20Android%20user%2C%20you%20have%20a%20little%20more%20to%20work%20with%3A%20You%20can%20access%20quick-reply%20features%2C%20and%20these%20only%20need%20Bluetooth%2C%20not%20voice%20assistant%2C%20so%20you%20can%20shoot%20a%20pre-set%20canned%20reply%20even%20if%20your%20phone%20is%20locked.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2219eb552f-c216-493f-a9ee-b57e153ef280%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22What%20we%20don't%20like%5C%22%3EWhy%20it's%20not%20worth%20%24150%20more%20than%20the%20Garmin%20Vivoactive%206%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EHaving%20tested%20both%20of%20these%20watches%20over%20the%20last%20three%20months%2C%20I%20can%20tell%20you%20Garmin's%20two%20smartwatches%20are%20very%2C%20very%20similar.%20The%20main%20difference%3A%20The%20Venu%203%20is%20slightly%20smarter%20but%20also%20significantly%20more%20expensive%20than%20the%20Vivoactive%206.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere's%20what%20%24150%20more%20will%20get%20you%20with%20the%20Venu%203%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EAbility%20to%20take%20phone%20calls%20on-wrist.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EAbility%20to%20use%20voice%20assistant%20and%20reply%20to%20incoming%20texts%20on-wrist.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EAbility%20to%20initiate%20pre-set%20texts%20on%20an%20Android%20on-wrist.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E14%20days%20of%20battery%20life%20vs.%2011%20days%20in%20the%20Vivoactive%206.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E30%20preloaded%20activity%20profiles%20vs.%2080%20in%20the%20Vivoactive%206.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ESlightly%20higher%20display%20resolution.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EA%20built-in%20barometric%20altimeter%20for%20more%20accurate%20elevation%20tracking.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20my%20opinion%2C%20unless%20you%20take%20quick%20phone%20calls%20a%20lot%20or%20use%20voice%20assistant%20all%20the%20time%20(and%20have%20your%20phone%20unlocked%20to%20do%20so)%2C%20the%20Vivoactive%206%20is%20a%20much%20better%20value%20for%20your%20money.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22db981032-b28d-4cbd-970e-9b1c46fd55e1%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22How%20it%20compares%5C%22%3EHow%20it%20compares%20to%20other%20smart%20watches%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20person%20wearing%20a%20green%20Garmin%20smartwatch%20checks%20their%20workout%20stats%20during%20a%20gym%20session.%20The%20watch%20screen%20displays%20heart%20rate%2C%20time%2C%20reps%2C%20active%20calories%2C%20and%20steps.%20Below%2C%20two%20dumbbells%20rest%20on%20a%20worn%20wooden%20box%2C%20with%20the%20person's%20shoes%20and%20workout%20space%20visible%20in%20the%20background.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68923de785e81483682f5131%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Vivoactive%206%2C%20shown%20here%2C%20is%20my%20pick%20for%20the%20best%20Garmin%20smartwatch%20for%20most%20people.%3Cp%3ERachael%20Schultz%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20are%20more%20interested%20in%20having%20a%20great%20smartwatch%20that%20does%20a%20%3Cem%3Egood-enough%3C%2Fem%3E%20job%20at%20tracking%20workouts%2C%20then%20your%20decision%20is%20really%20between%20the%20Garmin%20Venu%203%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbi-auto-15110262728aff-20%26h%3Dd24926bd6912ca510b213bc784fe95ff65dcee164810ef997c3642e94c2e4eb9%26postID%3D68939038ef1e672788f14066%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Ftech%252Fgarmin-venu-3-review%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.amazon.com%252FApple-Smartwatch-Aluminium-Fitness-Tracker%252Fdp%252FB0DGHNXP5Y%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EApple%20Watch%20Series%2010%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbi-auto-15110262728aff-20%26h%3D4ddea38e7a4431b6bbc892de4dd84b6be609f49cf9d5b546a340cb2d4ae578eb%26postID%3D68939038ef1e672788f14066%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Ftech%252Fgarmin-venu-3-review%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.amazon.com%252FGoogle-Pixel-Watch-Latest-Model%252Fdp%252FB0D91268TH%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGoogle%20Pixel%20Watch%203%3C%2Fa%3E.%20(After%20testing%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbi-auto-15110262728aff-20%26h%3Dcbfd7c509aebcb1a922509f0532cc17462239fcc98ad48fa6601be2e26f9d1c9%26postID%3D68939038ef1e672788f14066%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Ftech%252Fgarmin-venu-3-review%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.amazon.com%252FFitbit-Smartwatch-Readiness-Exercise-Tracking%252Fdp%252FB0B4MWCFV4%253Fth%253D1%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFitbit%20Versa%204%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20I%20can%20confirm%20it%20doesn't%20have%20a%20seat%20at%20this%20table.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAll%20three%20watches%20are%20a%20similar%20price%20(%24400%20to%20%24500)%2C%20have%20a%20sleek%20and%20clean%20design%2C%20and%20have%20an%20intense%2C%20visually%20rich%20display%20(the%20Venu%203%20and%20Pixel%203%20use%20AMOLED%2C%20while%20the%20Apple%20Watch%2010%20uses%20retina%20OLED).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Venu%203%20has%20a%20significantly%20longer%20battery%20life%20(14%20days%20vs.%2018-24%20hours)%2C%20a%20far%20more%20accurate%20GPS%2C%20and%20far%20more%20accurate%20heart%20rate%20sensor%20than%20either%20competitor.%20Overall%2C%20this%20means%20the%20Venu%203%20is%20going%20to%20be%20better%20at%20tracking%20your%20health%20and%20fitness%20and%20delivering%20deeper%2C%20more%20insightful%20metrics%20than%20the%20Apple%20Watch%20Series%2010%2C%20including%20personalized%20coaching%20for%20free%20in%20the%20Garmin%20app.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20said%2C%20the%20Apple%20Watch%20Series%2010%20does%20a%20good%20enough%20job%20at%20tracking%20workouts%20for%20most%20people%20(and%20auto-tracks%20them%2C%20which%20Garmins%20do%20not)%2C%20is%20very%20good%20at%20analyzing%20sleep%2C%20and%20is%20way%20better%20at%20being%20a%20smartwatch%20for%20iPhone%20users%20compared%20to%20the%20Venu%203.%20The%20Apple%20Watch%20integrates%20better%20with%20the%20iPhone%20ecosystem%2C%20so%20you%20have%20more%20apps%20on-wrist%20(including%20navigation%20from%20Apple%20Maps)%2C%20access%20to%20Siri%2C%20and%20voice%20control%20without%20needing%20to%20unlock%20your%20phone.%20You%20will%20have%20to%20charge%20it%20every%201-2%20days%2C%20though.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Pixel%20Watch%203%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20integrates%20much%20better%20with%20the%20Android%20ecosystem%20than%20the%20Venu%203%20%E2%80%94%20you%20can%20access%20more%20apps%20and%20Google%20Assistant%20from%20your%20wrist%20versus%20just%20receiving%20notifications%20and%20responding%20to%20texts%20and%20phone%20calls.%20The%20Pixel%20Watch%20is%20built%20on%20Fitbit's%20technology%2C%20so%20its%20workout%20and%20sleep%20tracking%20are%20pretty%20good%2C%20though%20it%20can't%20compete%20with%20Garmin's%20GPS%20or%20recovery%20insights.%20And%2C%20like%20the%20Apple%20Watches%2C%20the%20Pixel%203%20needs%20to%20be%20charged%20every%201-2%20days%20versus%20the%20Venu%203's%2014-day%20battery%20life.%20For%20more%20picks%2C%20check%20out%20our%20guide%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fbest-smartwatch%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ebest%20smartwatches%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fbest-fitness-tracker%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ebest%20fitness%20trackers%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%223e1677b4-6f02-4873-a2f4-1c26d6921875%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22The%20bottom%20line%5C%22%3EThe%20bottom%20line%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221300%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20close-up%20image%20of%20a%20Garmin%20Venu%203%20smartwatch%20on%20a%20person's%20wrist.%20The%20screen%20displays%20the%20Battery%20Manager%20settings%2C%20showing%20%26quot%3BBattery%20Saver%20Off%20(9%20Days)%2C%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BBattery%20%25%20On%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3BBattery%20Est.%20Off.%26quot%3B%20The%20watch%20has%20a%20white%20band%20and%20a%20round%20face%20with%20a%20black%20screen%20and%20metallic%20bezel.%5C