F%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThey%20are%20traumatised%20for%20life%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Roshni%20Perween%2C%20a%20victim%20of%20child%20marriage%20herself.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHailing%20from%20a%20small%20village%20of%20Simalbari%20of%20Kishanganj%2C%20Roshni%20was%20leading%20a%20regular%20life%20until%20she%20reached%20class%20nine.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSuddenly%2C%20my%20parents%20started%20getting%20a%20lot%20of%20marriage%20proposals%20for%20me.%20I%20had%20my%20whole%20future%20in%20front%20of%20me.%20I%20had%20not%20even%20completed%20my%20board%20exams.%20Despite%20a%20lot%20of%20opposition%2C%20I%20was%20married%20off%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20recalls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUpon%20reaching%20her%20new%20home%2C%20Roshni%20discovered%20that%20her%20husband%20was%2045%20years%20old%20%E2%80%94%20three%20times%20her%20age!%20%E2%80%9CI%20was%20very%20young%20and%20knew%20nothing%20about%20life%20after%20marriage.%20My%20husband%20forced%20himself%20on%20me%20and%20I%20was%20shocked%20to%20my%20core%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20three%20months%2C%20Roshni%20ran%20away%20and%20returned%20to%20her%20parents%E2%80%99%20home.%20%E2%80%9CSome%20time%20later%2C%20I%20found%20out%20that%20I%20was%20pregnant%20with%20his%20child.%20A%20few%20months%20later%2C%20I%20gave%20birth%20to%20my%20son.%20I%20was%20not%20ready%20to%20go%20back%20to%20that%20hell%2C%20but%20I%20was%20forced%20to%20return%20to%20his%20house.%20When%20I%20went%20back%2C%20my%20husband%20did%20not%20accept%20me%2C%20as%20I%20had%20been%20away%20for%20a%20year%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20facing%20unimaginable%20challenges%20and%20hardships%2C%20including%20rejection%20by%20her%20own%20family%20and%20societal%20stigma%2C%20Roshni%20refused%20to%20succumb%20to%20despair.%20She%20bravely%20walked%20away%20from%20an%20abusive%20marriage.%20At%2015%2C%20with%20the%20responsibility%20of%20raising%20a%20newborn%2C%20she%20started%20working