es%20in%20the%20past%20two%20years%2C%20transforming%20the%20lives%20of%20countless%20young%20girls%20in%20the%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Froshni-child-marriage-1727791803.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Roshni%20also%20helps%20young%20girls%20with%20skill%20development%20by%20enrolling%20them%20in%20several%20government%20schemes.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Froshni-child-marriage-1727791803.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Froshni-child-marriage-1727791803-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Froshni-child-marriage-1727791803-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Froshni-child-marriage-1727791803-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Froshni-child-marriage-1727791803-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-368389%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ERoshni%20also%20helps%20young%20girls%20with%20skill%20development%20by%20enrolling%20them%20in%20several%20government%20schemes.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E5%20steps%20towards%20combatting%20child%20marriage%20in%20India%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERoshni%20assists%20families%20of%20girls%20in%20availing%20welfare%20schemes%20such%20as%20housing%20under%20Indira%20Awaas%20Yojana%20and%20ration%20cards%20for%20Below%20Poverty%20Line%20(BPL)%20households.%20She%20also%20helps%20them%20with%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F481300%2Fm