20coated%20in%20metal%20or%20glass%2C%20can%20be%20fatal%20to%20birds%20flying%20in%20the%20sky%20%E2%80%94%20they%20can%20lose%20their%20wings%2C%20leaving%20them%20permanently%20grounded.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENadeem%20says%20that%20after%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F268302%2Famur-falcon-migratory-bird-threatened-iucn-hunting-nagaland-consrvation-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebeing%20injured%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20many%20of%20these%20birds%20end%20up%20in%20the%20gutters%20or%20on%20the%20roadside%2C%20where%20they%20are%20run%20over%20by%20vehicles%20or%20bleed%20to%20death.%20Otherwise%2C%20the%20trauma%20of%20being%20unable%20to%20fly%20is%20soon%20followed%20by%20death.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20fact%20that%20Chinese%20manjhas%20were%20banned%20by%20the%20government%20in%202017%2C%20conservationists%20end%20up%20rescuing%20thousands%20of%20birds%20from%20their%20clutches%20every%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20brothers%20came%20across%20the%20injured%20kite%2C%20they%20picked%20it%20up%20and%20rushed%20to%20the%20hospital.%20But%20they%20were%20met%20with%20refusal%20no%20matter%20where%20they%20went%2C%20recalls%20Nadeem%2C%20now%2044.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20knocked%20on%20the%20doors%20of%20several%20veterinary%20clinics.%20They%20told%20us%2C%20%E2%80%98We%20do%20not%20treat%20carnivorous%20birds%E2%80%99%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%20wp-image-277447%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F03%2FNadeem-bird-1646226487.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Wildlife%20Rescue%20NGO%20raptor%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F03%2FNadeem-bird-1646226487.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F03%2FNadeem-bird-1646226487-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F03%2FNadeem-bird-1646226487-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F03%2FNadeem-bird-1646226487-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F03%2FNadeem-bird-1646226487-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-277447%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EInjured%20birds%20during%20treatment.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnable%20to%20find%20a%20solution%2C%20the%20brothers%20returned%20the%20bird%20to%20the%20spot%20where%20they%20found%20it.%20But%20since%20then%2C%20they%20have%20come%20a%20long%20way.%20From%20their%20basement%2C%20they%20run%20a%20makeshift%20veterinary%20operation%20centre%20for%20injured%20and%20maimed%20birds%2C%20helping%20save%20thousands%20of%20birds%20to%20date.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ENavigating%20a%20death%20trap%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20their%20first%20encounter%20with%20the%20kite%2C%20Nadeem%20and%20Saud%20spent%20the%20next%20few%20years%20picking%20up%20other%20injured%20birds%20and%20placing%20them%20in%20safe%20places%20that%20will%20prevent%20them%20from%20being%20run%20over%20or%20choking%20in%20a%20gutter.%20But%20the%20fate%20of%20these%20birds%20would%20remain%20unknown.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20kept%20looking%20for%20help%2C%20but%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20find%20any%2C%E2%80%9D%20Nadeem%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202003%2C%20the%20siblings%20found%20another%20kite%20in%20a%20parking%20lot.%20This%20time%2C%20they%20decided%20to%20take%20a%20different%20approach.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20took%20it%20to%20a%20veterinarian%20who%20had%20treated%20our%20uncle%E2%80%99s%20dog.%20He%20agreed%20to%20help%20us%2C%20and%20we%20were%20able%20to%20save%20the%20bird%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%20then%20on%2C%20every%20injured%20bird%20they%20found%20was%20taken%20to%20the%20vet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COver%20time%2C%20the%20number%20of%20birds%20increased%20to%20the%20extent%20that%20we%20needed%20to%20buy%20a%20cage.%20We%20released%20the%20birds%20on%20the%20rooftop%20during%20the%20day%20and%20put%20them%20in%20the%20cage%20after%20dark.%20Our%20neighbours%20appreciated%20our%20efforts%20and%20started%20pitching%20in%20to%20help%2C%E2%80%9D%20Nadeem%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20adds%20that%20the%20number%20of%20injured%20birds%20grew%20so%20high%20that%20they%20eventually%20converted%20their%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F275250%2Fdelhi-nest-man-builds-bird-bamboo-homes-trains-students%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eroof%20into%20an%20enclosure%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20rescued%20almost%20400%20birds%2C%20including%20owls%2C%20hawks%2C%20water%20hens%2C%20and%20egrets%20between%202003%20and%202010.%20In%202010%2C%20we%20decided%20to%20set%20up%20an%20NGO%2C%20Wildlife%20Rescue%2C%20to%20take%20up%20the%20cause%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20then%2C%20the%20brothers%20say%20they%20have%20saved%20over%2023%2C000%20birds%20from%20more%20than%20100%20species.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20cater%20to%20at%20least%2040%20species%20each%20year%2C%20and%20have%20100%20healing%20birds%20at%20our%20rooftop%20on%20any%20given%20day%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%20wp-image-277450%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F03%2FNadeem-surgery-1646226507.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Wildlife%20Rescue%20NGO%20raptor%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F03%2FNadeem-surgery-1646226507.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F03%2FNadeem-surgery-1646226507-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F03%2FNadeem-surgery-1646226507-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F03%2FNadeem-surgery-1646226507-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F03%2FNadeem-surgery-1646226507-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-277450%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EAn%20injured%20bird%20undergoing%20surgery.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENadeem%20and%20Saud%20also%20collect%20birds%20from%20all%20hospitals%20in%20the%20surrounding%20areas.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20receive%20calls%20from%20locals%2C%20the%20Delhi%20Police%2C%20the%20fire%20service%20department%2C%20and%20civic%20body%20officials.%20They%20spot%20the%20birds%20and%20hand%20them%20over%20to%20us%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENadeem%20notes%20that%20the%20rescued%20birds%20have%20all%20sorts%20of%20injuries%20or%20diseases.%20%E2%80%9CAt%20times%2C%20the%20cuts%20are%20minor.%20Otherwise%2C%20some%20birds%20sustain%20serious%20injuries.%20Some%20have%20gynaecological%20issues%2C%20such%20as%20eggs%20getting%20stuck%20while%20delivering.%20On%20other%20occasions%2C%20the%20chicks%20fall%20from%20the%20nest%20or%20juveniles%20get%20injured%20while%20learning%20how%20to%20fly%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20adds%20that%20the%20bird%20species%20who%20come%20in%20for%20treatment%20also%20vary%20with%20season.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20kite%20bird%20season%20starts%20from%20March%2C%20and%20there%20will%20be%20at%20least%20500%20injured%20kites%20in%20the%20next%20two%20months.%20The%20number%20of%20rescued%20hawk%20birds%20will%20increase%20more%20during%20mid-summer.%20The%20highest%20number%20of%20birds%20are%20injured%20in%20August%2C%20as%20the%20number%20of%20people%20flying%20kites%20peaks%20during%20Independence%20Day%20celebrations%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENadeem%20says%20all%20the%20rescued%20birds%20are%20given%20balanced%20food%20with%20meat%20in%20their%20diet%20and%20treated%20by%20an%20expert%20veterinarian.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMany%20birds%20recover%20and%20fly%2C%20while%20the%20birds%20with%20severe%20injuries%20feel%20highly%20stressed%20and%20die.%20Birds%20are%20psychologically%20vulnerable%2C%20and%20the%20trauma%20severely%20affects%20their%20health%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EProtecting%20the%20ecosystem%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Nadeem%20and%20Saud%E2%80%99s%20cause%20is%20noble%2C%20they%20do%20not%20have%20any%20formal%20education%20in%20wildlife%20rescue.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20quit%20school%20in%201997%20as%20our%20family%E2%80%99s%20financial%20condition%20could%20not%20allow%20us%20to%20study%20further.%20Our%20parents%20wanted%20us%20to%20revive%20their%20business%2C%20so%20we%20started%20working%20at%20our%20bathroom%20fittings%20shop%2C%E2%80%9D%20Nadeem%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%20wp-image-277448%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F03%2FNadeem-cage-1646226504.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Wildlife%20Rescue%20NGO%20raptor%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F03%2FNadeem-cage-1646226504.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F03%2FNadeem-cage-1646226504-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F03%2FNadeem-cage-1646226504-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F03%2FNadeem-cage-1646226504-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F03%2FNadeem-cage-1646226504-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-277448%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ERooftop%20at%20Nadeem%E2%80%99s%20house%20that%20works%20as%20an%20enclosure.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESaud%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20work%20for%20our%20social%20cause%20in%20our%20free%20time.%20We%20have%20a%20team%20of%20a%20part-time%20veterinarian%2C%20and%20two%20persons%20who%20tend%20the%20birds%20and%20take%20care%20of%20the%20paperwork.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20duo%20often%20visit%20the%20US%20to%20receive%20training%20in%20and%20attend%20workshops%20on%20wildlife%20rescue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWildlife%20rescue%20is%20entirely%20different%20from%20biology%2C%20and%20there%20is%20no%20formal%20course%20in%20India%20that%20addresses%20it.%20The%20US%20is%20one%20of%20the%20most%20advanced%20places%20and%20is%20known%20for%20its%20commendable%20work%20in%20bird%20rescue.%20We%20learn%20new%20techniques%20and%20train%20ourselves%20with%20help%20from%20experts%20at%20various%20wildlife%20centres%20across%20the%20country%2C%E2%80%9D%20Saud%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20many%20years%2C%20the%20brothers%20were%20using%20their%20own%20savings%20to%20fuel%20operations.%20In%20recent%20years%2C%20donations%20from%20kind%20strangers%20have%20helped%20ease%20the%20financial%20burden.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESaud%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20been%20receiving%20donations%20for%20the%20past%20five%20years.%20These%20partly%20support%20our%20cause.%20Otherwise%2C%20it%20is%20challenging%20to%20manage%20all%20the%20expenses%20from%20our%20earnings.%20We%20have%20also%20registered%20an%20NGO%2C%20Raptor%20Rescue%20and%20Research%20Inc%2C%20to%20raise%20funds%20in%20the%20US%20and%20help%20our%20cause%20in%20India.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%2040-year-old%20notes%20that%20the%20NGO%20needs%20more%20financial%20support.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20run%20on%20a%20limited%20budget.%20Many%20bird%20rescue%20calls%20coming%20from%20far%20corners%20of%20Delhi%20go%20unanswered.%20We%20do%20not%20have%20an%20ambulance%20and%20cannot%20travel%20far%20to%20rescue%20birds.%20Many%20people%20who%20wish%20to%20help%20us%20cannot%20bring%20them%20to%20our%20house%20for%20logistical%20reasons.%20Some%20fear%20handling%20birds%20of%20prey.%20Reaching%20out%20to%20birds%20from%20far-flung%20areas%20is%20difficult.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESaud%20adds%20that%20receiving%20donations%20will%20help%20them%20cater%20to%20a%20farther%20geographic%20area.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20can%20manage%20other%20daily%20issues%20and%20challenges%20at%20our%20end%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20siblings%20plan%20to%20establish%20a%20full-fledged%20hospital%20for%20birds.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20rented%20a%20small%20clinic%2C%20and%20more%20donations%20will%20help%20us%20build%20an%20adequate%20facility%20for%20the%20birds.%20Talks%20are%20also%20underway%20to%20receive%20a%20piece%20of%20land%20from%20the%20government%20for%20the%20hospital%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed%20wp-block-embed-youtube%20wp-embed-aspect-16-9%20wp-has-aspect-ratio%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed__wrapper%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Ciframe%20data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll%20data-origheight%3D%5C%22270%5C%22%20allowfullscreen%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2F_ha9nKYlwqQ%3Fenablejsapi%3D1%26autoplay%3D0%26cc_load_policy%3D0%26cc_lang_pref%3D%26iv_load_policy%3D3%26loop%3D0%26rel%3D0%26fs%3D1%26playsinline%3D1%26autohide%3D2%26theme%3Ddark%26color%3Dred%26controls%3D1%26%5C%22%20data-no-lazy%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20player%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22480%5C%22%20data-origwidth%3D%5C%22480%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22270%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUrvi%20Gupta%2C%20a%20Delhi-based%20researcher%20at%20Wildlife%20Institute%20of%20India%20(WII)%2C%20says%20saving%20raptors%20is%20imp