ards.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExplaining%20how%20that%20part%20of%20her%20life%20shaped%20up%2C%20she%20shares%2C%20%E2%80%9CMy%20sister%2C%20a%20filmmaker%20and%20potter%2C%20often%20visited%20this%20piece%20of%20land%3B%20she%20would%20convince%20me%20to%20take%20a%20look%20at%20it.%20Her%20descriptions%20made%20me%20curious%20%E2%80%94%20%E2%80%98Rhododendrons%20bloom%20here%20in%20summer%3B%20the%20air%20is%20so%20crisp%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%94%20I%20finally%20agreed%20to%20go%20check%20out%20the%20place.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndependence%20Day%202004%20saw%20Sheela%20and%20Rajeev%20standing%20on%20the%20land%2C%20which%20is%20now%20christened%20as%20Jilling%20Terraces.%20The%20silence%20was%20magical%3B%20broken%20only%20by%20birds.%20They%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20seem%20to%20look%20away%3B%20they%20knew%20they%E2%80%99d%20found%20%E2%80%98home%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FJilling-Terraces-2_11zon-1754579486.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Jilling%20Terraces%20is%20a%20couple%20of%20hours%20away%20from%20Nainital%20%C2%A0in%20the%20South%20Gola%20range%20of%20Himalayas%2C%20with%20stunning%20views%20of%20Nanda%20Devi%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FJilling-Terraces-2_11zon-1754579486.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FJilling-Terraces-2_11zon-1754579486-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FJilling-Terraces-2_11zon-1754579486-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FJilling-Terraces-2_11zon-1754579486-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FJilling-Terraces-2_11zon-1754579486-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-483495%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EJilling%20Terraces%20is%20a%20couple%20of%20hours%20away%20from%20Nainital%20%C2%A0in%20the%20South%20Gola%20range%20of%20Himalayas%2C%20with%20stunning%20views%20of%20Nanda%20Devi%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20stayed%20around%20the%20area%20for%20a%20week.%20Every%20morning%2C%20we%E2%80%99d%20wake%20up%20thinking%2C%20%E2%80%98This%20is%20%3Cem%3Eliterally%20%3C%2Fem%3Ethe%20most%20beautiful%20place%E2%80%99.%20We%20were%20gripped%20by%20the%20dream%2C%E2%80%9D%20Sheela%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20who%20was%20most%20excited%20about%20the%20plausibility%20of%20turning%20this%20land%20into%20%E2%80%98home%E2%80%99%20was%20the%20architect%20in%20her.%20%E2%80%9CArchitects%20are%20perpetually%20dreaming%3B%20they%20would%20build%20in%20the%20clouds%20if%20they%20could.%20The%20challenge%20is%20that%20in%20cities%2C%20we%20rarely%20get%20the%20freedom%20to%20really%20go%20all%20out%20and%20create%20what%20we%E2%80%99d%20like%20to.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20her%2C%20the%20land%20was%20like%20a%20blank%20slate%20waiting%20to%20be%20filled%20with%20possibility.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20excitement%20%E2%80%94%20combined%20with%20the%20relief%20of%20their%20Delhi-weary%20lungs%20finally%20breathing%20cleaner%20air%20%E2%80%94%20led%20Sheela%20and%20Rajeev%20to%20embrace%20the%20idea%20of%20a%20homestay.%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F332168%2Ftadoba-maharashtra-vacation-sustainable-homestay-by-wildlife-conservation-experts%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENestled%20in%20a%20cocoon%20of%20green%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Jilling%20Terraces%20is%20a%20charming%20time-warp%20with%20echoes%20of%20the%20colonial%20era.%20%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20literally%20at%20the%20top%20of%20the%20clouds.%20You%20have%20to%20see%20to%20believe